            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "GRAND SEASONS展銷廳辦親子活動 吸逾300家庭客參與",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"GRAND SEASONS展銷廳辦親子活動 吸逾300家庭客參與\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7154aee56402b3763c4bd5dc3b8f8aba/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041817374763892.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">GRAND SEASONS展銷廳辦親子活動 吸逾300家庭客參與</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>會德豐地產發展的將軍澳日出康城GRAND SEASONS展銷廳，趁復活佳節，舉辦「復活節限定親子活動」，讓睇樓客及小朋友感受項目全方位親子休閒體驗，吸引逾300家庭客參與。\n\n</p>\n<p>會德豐地產副主席兼常務董事黃光耀表示， SEASONS系列承2024年新盤銷量冠軍之勢，加上《財政預算案》利好經濟及樓市措施，SEASONS系列最近一個月速售62伙，幾乎日日有成交，套現逾3.6億元，銷情熾熱。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4202990/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f54aeb63d24da22ac3bba500ae04e7f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-18_at_17_23_02.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4202991/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d43f0c681bd9a750b1effdba5084a528/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-18_at_17_23_03_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4202992/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bc94306020c4577b6d699755800c6a17/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-18_at_17_23_03_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4202993/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57919c82c461ed0a3488fc9ab004175e/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-18_at_17_23_03.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4202995/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96e4a74339ade56c87d0c2c9bcec59a6/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-18_at_17_23_04.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4202996/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a63ac463130827339f5da00cfae58667/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-18_at_17_23_05_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4202997/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82aa28adcdca9f4ecd6b86b4d9284d6c/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-18_at_17_23_05.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>展銷廳專設全新「Sakura 櫻海季樂廳、Herb Garden 種植園及SPARK」主題區，更特別換上色彩繽紛的復活節裝飾，變身成為打卡熱點。今日活動更特別邀請香港兒童探索博物館（CDM）精心策劃「創意懸浮彩光復活蛋工作坊」—結合科學、創意及復活節元素，讓家長和小朋友一同發揮創意。一眾家長表示項目設施多元化，特別欣賞項目引入全方位兒童發展概念SPARK，能推動小朋友在互動玩樂中學習，亦能增進親子關係。同場亦有社企Mindful Sparks提供春日果香精釀氣泡茶，讓來賓享受歡樂難忘的復活節假期。  \n\n</p>\n<p>SEASONS 系列自開售以來深受家庭客青睞，其一大亮點是引入了會德豐首創的全方位兒童發展概念SPARK及其主題兒童設施，由香港兒童探索博物館(CDM) 擔任設計及活動顧問，讓小住戶在生活中體驗「兒童主導遊玩」，啟發兒童全方位發展。而區內亦配備約20萬方呎日出公園及動感公園等豐富的親子及綠化空間，並鄰近多所知名中小學及香港科技大學，提供優越家庭生活配套。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
